Title: Break Them Out
Description:
Cages, chains and transportation carts... I think we all know where this leads.

If the drakonids plan on capturing and enslaving the slitherdrakes, then they are no better than the djaradin. 

See what you can do to thwart their plans.
ObjectivesText: Disrupt the poachers and stop them from capturing the slitherdrakes.
